 three vehicles, which is what? Our joy, our devotion, really just recognizing out of all

00:01:13.480 --> 00:01:20.400
 the situations that are possible, we're free of so many circumstances and habitual patterns

00:01:20.400 --> 00:01:26.880
 that would prevent us to be reflecting on our own beautiful nature and trying to bring

00:01:26.880 --> 00:01:32.720
 those qualities up in our own minds and hearts for the benefit of all. Just really appreciating

00:01:32.720 --> 00:01:42.880
 that and then of course, and then really connecting with a mind and heart, just vast bodhicitta,

00:01:42.880 --> 00:01:50.880
 which is the essence of Mahayana, both generating it and actualizing it, really truly aspiring

00:01:50.880 --> 00:01:57.720
 that in this precious moment, it can really bring benefit to limitless beings beyond any

00:01:57.720 --> 00:02:05.320
