00:08:49.120 --> 00:08:56.640
 increasing our joy, appreciation, our bodhicitta, we're also purifying our obscurations and

00:08:56.640 --> 00:09:02.920
 mistakes, purifying the ultimate mistake we have, which is not recognizing our nature,

