 getting caught up and tangled up in our conceptions and our hopes and our fears, dragging them

00:09:08.280 --> 00:09:16.680
 around in all kinds of drama and boringness, etc., etc., but purifying that, so purifying

00:09:16.680 --> 00:09:22.480
 the ultimate mistake we have, which is just simply not recognizing our nature, through

00:09:22.480 --> 00:09:28.840
 the skillful means of the Vajrasattva practice, and then also purifying all the relative abstains

00:09:28.840 --> 00:09:37.200
 and mistakes and obscurations we have, again, all the way from our most common, rough, emotional,

00:09:37.200 --> 00:09:44.200
 and karmic obscurations that we're creating, kind of passing them, purifying them through

00:09:44.200 --> 00:09:51.200
 to our more subtle knowledge obscurations and very subtle habitual patterns are being purified

